Program: The History Hour
Title: Boris Yeltsin's Surprise Resignation
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/w3csvsv4
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 7 Jan 2018
Mrs Yeltsin, on the day her husband shocked the world, half a century since the Mafia's grip on America was exposed, the 1999 protests in Iran - the biggest since the revolution - a student tells us how a photograph led to his death sentence and the Brazilian woman hijacker who took her kids along for the ride. Show less